{"tid":914414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖7年提分手摩洛哥女分屍男友煮飯派街坊","createTime":"2018-11-24T08:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T08:55:20.000Z","uid":221589,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"81bd8b096dae029224575767d31a2e2dc7028f5a","tid":914414,"uid":221589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:51:57.000Z","msg":"人肉叉燒飯！<br />\n<br />\n阿拉伯聯合酋長國（阿聯酋）最近發生宗慘無人道的命案，一名摩洛哥女子竟然將男友「煮成飯」，再分送給地盤工人吃，警方3個月後才發現事件。據了解，女子因分手而行兇。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，該名摩洛哥女子3個月前謀殺男友後碎屍，並將屍塊以果汁機攪碎，煮成當地傳統料理「machboos」（以米飯與肉為材料的阿拉伯傳統料理），再分送給住附近的巴基斯坦籍工人吃。<br />\n<br />\n死者的兄弟因與他失聯已久，故報警求助警方在女子家中的果汁機中發現一顆牙齒經DNA鑑定後證實是死者。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，女子向警方表示與男友交往7年，一直負擔大部分開支，但男友竟提出分手並準備與另一名女子結婚，因此想要作出報復女子正在被警方扣押待開庭受審。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女人"},{"pid":"6ac0c3f53c4afe43d849fe73e25aee0c565d15d1","tid":914414,"uid":135066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:52:49.000Z","msg":"人肉叉燒包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49a9eb136606b1e31dc9d68877dedf8d7267ec5","tid":914414,"uid":187076,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f6Jti0T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff6Jti0T.jpg&h=c03d2e01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"add32e8a086b34c34cad31ac74fcace2501db7f8","tid":914414,"uid":221589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e49a9eb136606b1e31dc9d68877dedf8d7267ec5","tid":914414,"uid":187076,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f6Jti0T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff6Jti0T.jpg&h=c03d2e01&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/epdMP74.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FepdMP74.png&h=5ee2544d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}